"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-25-olympic-legend-sir-steve-redgrave-very-shocked-charlotte-dujardin-video-21293634\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Sir Steve Redgrave says he was 'very shocked' to learn about the video of Charlotte Dujardin 'excessively' whipping a horse and it's 'probably right' that the dressage rider is suspended for theParis2024Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Redgrave\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sir Steve Redgrave\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Redgrave\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Redgrave\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 61, \"to\": 70}, {\"ngram\": \"Charlotte Dujardin\", \"from\": 74, \"to\": 92}, {\"ngram\": \"a horse\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 123}, {\"ngram\": \"the dressage rider\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 173}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis2024Olympics\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just days out from the Games, Dujardin - Britain's joint-most decorated female Olympian -released a statement confirming her withdrawalafter a video came to light which showed her making 'an error of judgement' during a coaching session.\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 255, \"end\": 262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9988213285336964, \"rank\": 0.0011320510520435277, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 293, \"end\": 301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999940883, \"rank\": 5.845383778756665e-12, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 242}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 323}, {\"ngram\": \"her withdrawalafter\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 354}, {\"ngram\": \"a video\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 362}, {\"ngram\": \"light\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"an error\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 410}, {\"ngram\": \"judgement\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 423}, {\"ngram\": \"a coaching session\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That shocking footage, filmed four years ago, was released on Wednesdayand the 39-year-old three-time gold-medallist has now been banned for six months by the International Federation for Equestrian Sports (FEI).\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 660, \"end\": 663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.639438477625331e-32, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That shocking footage\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 474}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesdayand\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"the 39-year-old three-time gold-medallist\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 569}, {\"ngram\": \"six months\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 604}, {\"ngram\": \"the International Federation\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"Equestrian Sports\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In its statement, the FEI declared that Dujardin had engaged 'in conduct contrary to the principles of horse welfare' during the training session which occurred at a private stable.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 689, \"end\": 692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.639438477625331e-32, 