ia.org/resource/Charlotte_Motor_Speedway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Motor_Speedway\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the news\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"our history\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"the five-time gold medallist\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'By the sounds of it, she's absolutely devastated by the situation she's found herself in.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sounds\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"the situation\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's probably the right thing that she's been suspended.'\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right thing\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser thatsupports HTML5 video Up Next Dujardin's fianc\\u00e9, Dean Wyatt-Golding, speaking out the couple's home on Wednesday, said they would be cooperating fully with the FEI while awaiting further updates on the situation.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1390, \"end\": 1400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.184942203000417e-16, \"text\": \"JavaScript\", \"types\": [\"Q9143\", \"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\"}, {\"begin\": 1462, \"end\": 1467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"score\": 0.9999999999536158, \"rank\": 4.6389053859243183e-11, \"text\": \"HTML5\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\"}, {\"begin\": 1511, \"end\": 1515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9999902344829279, \"rank\": 9.758993528569898e-06, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.639438477625331e-32, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this video\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"a web browser\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1441}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin's fianc\\u00e9\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1492}, {\"ngram\": \"the couple's home\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1557}, {\"ngram\": \"the FEI\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"the situation\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I can not say anything beyond Charlotte's statement.\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1707, \"end\": 1716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Motor_Speedway\", \"score\": 0.7818487832077666, \"rank\": 0.24406826747532892, \"text\": \"Charlotte\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Motor_Speedway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Motor_Speedway\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All we can do is wait and see what happens,' he said.\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'All we can do is wait and see what happens.'\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked how the footage may have been shared, he replied: 'No, we have no idea.\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1909, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the footage\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1853}, {\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Charlotte is obviously cooperating with the equestrian authorities for now.'\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1912, \"end\": 1921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Motor_Speedway\", \"score\": 0.7818487832077666, \"rank\": 0.24406826747532892, \"text\": \"Charlotte\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Motor_Speedway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Motor_Speedway\"}, {\"begin\": 1956, \"end\": 1966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.8280039820110543, \"rank\": 0.20772365972045695, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A video has emerged from four years ago which shows me making an error of judgement during a coaching session.\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2100, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A video\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"an error\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"judgement\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"a coaching session\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Understandably, the International Federation for Equestrian Sports (FEI) is investigating and I have made the decision to withdraw from all competition - including the Paris Olympics - while this process takes place.\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2170, \"end\": 2173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.639438477625331e-32, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the International Federation\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"Equestrian Sports\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2168}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2220}, {\"ngram\": \"all competition\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2253}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2284}, {\"ngram\": \"this process\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What happened was completely out of character and does not reflect how I train my horses or coach my pupils, however there is no excuse.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2456, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"character\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2365}, {\"ngram\": \"my horses\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"my pupils\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"no excuse\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am deeply ashamed and should have set a better example in that moment.\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a better example\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2513}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sincerely sorry for my actions and devastated that I have let everyone down, including Team GB, fans and sponsors.\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2623, \"end\": 2630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9976655407092376, \"rank\": 0.002265983319418568, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my actions\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2566}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsors\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will cooperate fully with the FEI, British Equestrian Federation and British Dressage during their investigations, and will not be commenting further until the process is complete.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2684, \"end\": 2687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.639438477625331e-32, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2689, \"end\": 2718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Equestrian Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 2723, \"end\": 2739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Dressage\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their investigations\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2767}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Charlotte Dujardin, 23rd July 2024.\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2836, \"end\": 2854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Dujardin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Explaining the timing of the video's release, Dutch Equine lawyer Stephan Wensing, who is acting on behalf of an anonymous whistleblower, said his client simply 'could not bring themselves to allow Dujardin to win medals at the Olympics'.\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 3111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2919, \"end\": 2924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.9913062521146272, \"rank\": 0.007615558737879068, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2939, \"end\": 2946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eline_Heger\", \"score\": 0.6581589501824835, \"rank\": 0.5192817811907153, \"text\": \"Stephan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eline_Heger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eline_Heger\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the timing\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2894}, {\"ngram\": \"the video's release\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2917}, {\"ngram\": \"behalf\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2979}, {\"ngram\": \"an anonymous whistleblower\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 3009}, {\"ngram\": \"his client\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3026}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin\", \"from\": 3071, \"to\": 3079}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3093}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3097, \"to\": 3109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's unacceptable that dressage sport should be accompanied by animal abuse,' Wensing said.\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3205, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dressage sport\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3151}, {\"ngram\": \"animal abuse\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3189}, {\"ngram\": \"Wensing\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'If top-level sport can only be performed in such a way that the welfare of the horse is compromised, then top-level sport should be abolished.\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3350, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"top-level sport\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"such a way\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3262}, {\"ngram\": \"the welfare\", \"from\": 3268, \"to\": 3279}, {\"ngram\": \"the horse\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3292}, {\"ngram\": \"top-level sport\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Everyone who deals with horses has their own responsibility in this, and this also applies to bystanders who become aware of excesses.'\", \"from\": 3352, \"to\": 3488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3361}, {\"ngram\": \"horses\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3383}, {\"ngram\": \"their own responsibility\", \"from\": 3388, \"to\": 3412}, {\"ngram\": \"bystanders\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3457}, {\"ngram\": \"excesses\", \"from\": 3478, \"to\": 3486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wensing added: 'Equestrian sport must regulate itself and ensure that there can never be a discussion about horse welfare in sport again.\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3506, \"end\": 3522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equestrian sport\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wensing\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3497}, {\"ngram\": \"a discussion\", \"from\": 3579, \"to\": 3591}, {\"ngram\": \"horse welfare\", \"from\": 3598, \"to\": 3611}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This is a very important task for the jury members who have lost sight of the core value of dressage for far too long and have overvalued spastic movements of horses.\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3796, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very important task\", \"from\": 3638, \"to\": 3659}, {\"ngram\": \"the jury members\", \"from\": 3664, \"to\": 3680}, {\"ngram\": \"sight\", \"from\": 3695, \"to\": 370